---
// Hero component for overseas bank account closure service
---

<section
  class="p-6 pt-14 sm:p-12"
  itemscope
  itemtype="https://schema.org/Service"
>
  <div
    class="animate-reveal-from-left-600 relative h-[calc(100vh-6rem)] rounded-2xl bg-[url(../assets/images/hero_sm.jpg)] bg-cover bg-bottom-left bg-no-repeat md:h-[calc(100svh-6rem)] md:bg-[url(../assets/images/hero.jpg)]"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 flex translate-y-15 items-center p-6 md:translate-y-30 md:justify-start md:pl-12"
    >
      <div>
        <h2
          class="animate-slide-in-left-800 from-primary-500 to-primary-700 mb-2 bg-gradient-to-r bg-clip-text text-[5.3vw] font-bold text-transparent drop-shadow-[2px_2px_4px_rgba(255,255,255,0.8)] md:mb-4 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl"
          itemprop="name"
        >
          海外口座、<br />凍結口座放置していませんか？
        </h2>
        <h3
          class="animate-slide-in-left-800 animate-delay-200 text-sm font-semibold text-orange-400 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
        >
          <strong>
            現地渡航不要！英語力不要！<br
              class="block md:hidden"
            />面倒な解約手続きをプロが完全サポート
          </strong>
        </h3>
        <!-- 全額返金バッジ -->
        <div class="animate-slide-in-left-800 animate-delay-300 mt-3 md:mt-4">
          <div
            class="inline-block rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-600 px-4 py-2 text-white shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm md:px-6 md:py-3"
          >
            <span class="text-sm font-bold tracking-wide md:text-lg">
              口座解約できなければ全額返金！
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 rounded-tl-xl bg-white pt-4 pr-0 pb-0 pl-6 text-right sm:rounded-tl-2xl sm:pt-6 sm:pl-8"
    >
      <ul
        class="animate-slide-in-left-800 animate-delay-500 from-primary-500 to-primary-700 mb-2 bg-gradient-to-r bg-clip-text text-base font-bold text-transparent md:mb-3 md:text-xl"
      >
        <li>
          <strong>現地に行かずに、閉じられます！</strong>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>
            もちろん口座内の預金は
            <br class="block md:hidden" />
            ご指定の銀行口座に送金可能
          </strong>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p
        class="animate-slide-in-left-800 animate-delay-800 text-sm md:text-base"
      >
        口座凍結・州政府移管・相続手続き…
        <br />
        複雑な海外口座の問題を、
        <br class="block md:hidden" />
        実績多数の専門チームが解決します。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
